Measurable indicator:  •Benefit sharing trends for the transboundary PAs;
Description and unit of measurement and disaggregation:  Amount of revenue (USD) received per PA plotted against time (years). Presented as either a line graph or bar graph;
As a result, there was a slight drop in revenue sharing amounts due to complete suspension of tourism in all PAs in 2021 as consequence of COVID 19 pandemic.

